          <h2>Exploring NLP with Game of Thrones: Social Networks  <span class="post-tag article">article</span></h2>
          <p>For this project, I wanted to explore the interactions between characters in the Game of Thrones Universe. Over the course of the show, relationships between characters change - friends become foes and acquaintances grow to form alliances. My goal for this project was to pick up on the changes in these relationships by using Social Network Analysis (SNA).</p>
          <img class="center" src="img/social_nx_ex1.png" alt="The resulting social network graph is shown" align="middle">
          <a href="blogs/game_of_thrones_social_network_nlp.html" class="button">Read On!</a>
